DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Someone has gone to a great amount of trouble to clear this section of
mountainous terrain of its stones. Within a dirt plot are two headstones
lovingly kept up by the diligent work of someone who cares a great deal
about them. Pliant branches from pine trees have been carefully crafted
into large wreaths and then placed in front of each headstone. The back
wall of the cabin is a soothing presence to the south.
*DESCRIPTION_END
