*DESCRIPTION_START
A crackling fireplace throws a cozy light across the interior of the cabin.
Hand-worked wooden boards have been placed across the dirt floor and the
plush skin of a white mountain bear covers most of the floor space in front
of the brick fireplace. It is evident that a lot of care has gone into the
construction and maintenance of this small home. The furnishings, a table,
some chairs and a sitting chair have all been hand-crafted. The wooden
door, leading back outside, hangs slightly ajar.
*DESCRIPTION_END
