NAME Shartan
MOUNTAIN
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Small rocks clatter down the rise to the south as you make your way along
the treacherous path leadings towards the looming Keep of Lynieas. The
Keep sits atop a tall plateau, pressed up against the side of the mountains.
A wide gorge runs from east to west in front of the keep, but you think that
you can see the signs of a bridge from here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT D 2252
