NUMBER 2257
NAME Shartan, gorge
MOUNTAIN
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The wind whistles fiercely through an east-west running gorge. Across the
gorge lies Lynieas Keep, a brooding structure designed with defense in
mind. A wooden bridge spans the wind-swept gorge.
*DESCRIPTION_END
