NUMBER 2261
NAME Keep, crypt
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
An aura of peace and solitude grace this place. The room is
large, designed to accommodate many sarcophagi, yet only three
are here. All three are closed and each bears a plaque engraved
with delicate silver writing. A stone bench off to one side
allows a place of quiet contemplation. The southern wall is
carved to portray Rorin leading warriors down a long tunnel that
leads to the afterlife. A circular stairway travels up into the
main portion of the keep.
*DESCRIPTION_END
