NUMBER 2262
NAME Lynieas Keep
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Many bright banners hang from the walls here, the two most
prominent being the golden dragon of Lynieas and those of the King
of Fayd. The main hall of Lynieas Keep is lined with beautiful
pillars and silk tapestries. A huge table made from the finest
woods sits in the middle of the hall, surrounded by several
ornate and well decorated chairs. Images of decisions and happy
celebrations long past, flood your mind as you gaze around this
hall. A stout wooden door leads out on to the keep courtyard, a
circular stairway rises into the well lit second floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
