*DESCRIPTION_START
White silk and cream colored ruffles make up the canopy on an
enormous bed in the center of this room. The four posts and
headboard are each carved with exquisite scrolling patterns. Two
large chairs, with black leather upholstery, are placed before a
stone fireplace which extends the full length of the back wall.
