ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand between the inner walls of the keep and the huge outer
walls. Several fruit bearing trees line the passageway here and
a curtain of emerald colored vines, hangs from a newly rebuilt
tower that guards the eastern side of the keep. As you look up
upon the fortifications you see several guards making rounds,
ready at all times for an attack. A sturdy wooden door leads
inside the tower.
*DESCRIPTION_END
