*DESCRIPTION_START
You see the massive inner gates which guard the courtyard here.
Glancing up you see several guards pacing the fortifications
watching for any sign of danger. The huge iron gates can be
braced by large wooden beams  which rest to one side of the
western wall. A large stone stairway leads up on to the ramparts.
*DESCRIPTION_END
