ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You sink into the softness of this luxurious bed, sliding between
jasmine scented silk sheets that caress your skin. You nestle in
the warmth of the down comforter and rest your head upon the soft
embroidered pillows. Feelings of warmth and bliss surround you as
the day's stress vanishes.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2282
