NUMBER 2295
NAME Lynieas Keep, Fortifications
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand upon the stone fortifications which guard the eastern
side of the keep. A huge catapult sits in one corner of the wall
here. Stacked around the catapult you see supplies for flaming
pitch, and many large iron balls. The catapult is pointed towards
a small clearing outside the walls, to the northeast of the keep.
A narrow walkway goes to the northern battlements. A granite
stairway leads back down to the courtyard.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT NW 2296
