NUMBER 2296
NAME Lynieas Keep, Northern battlements
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Two huge ballista stand at opposite ends on the northern walls.
Each is mounted upon a cleverly constructed turrent which allows
them to easily target anything approaching from the north. Giant
spears lay stacked along te sides of each weapon. Towards the
north, beyond several mountains, you see the great plains of ice,
homeland to the many barbarian tribes the keep guards against. A
narrow walkway leads to the eastern battlements.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT SE 2295
;
