ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand inside the barracks for the guardsmen of keep Lynieas.
Many cots and tables line this room. Next to each cot is a small
rack of well oiled weapons and a chest for their personal
belongings. Two heavy wooden doors lead out into the courtyard, a
small passageway goes from the barracks into the kitchens.
*DESCRIPTION_END
