ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand on metal grates in between the huge interior and
exterior gates to the keep. The walls of the fortress surround
you on three sides. The ceiling has several small holes from
which flaming pitch can be hurled down upon foes trying to break
into the keep. There is a grim warlike feeling here that both
comforts and worries you at the same time.
*DESCRIPTION_END
