NUMBER 3793
NAME Library Annex
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This chamber is a startling contrast to the rest of the Keep, being full
of assorted technological gadgets that emit strange noises and lights.
The centerpiece of the room is a large contraption with various panels,
levers and slots arrayed in a seemingly haphazard fashion across its
exterior. Scattered around the edges of the room is the packing material,
pieces of wood and paper, from which this technological apparatus was
birthed. A small arch leads back to the more comfortable environs of the
Keep library.
*DESCRIPTION_END
